1
00:00:05,832 --> 00:00:11,998
<i>A long time ago, a powerful demon fox</i>
<i>appeared with nine tails.</i>

2
00:00:12,906 --> 00:00:13,930
<i>With its powerful tails,</i>

3
00:00:14,007 --> 00:00:17,135
<i>it could smash mountains</i>
<i>and create tidal waves.</i>

4
00:00:17,710 --> 00:00:22,511
<i>A band of Ninjas rose to</i>
<i>defend their village from attack.</i>

5
00:00:22,949 --> 00:00:25,543
We have to wait until
the Fourth Hokage gets here!

6
00:00:25,785 --> 00:00:28,117
We can't let it get any closer
to our village!

7
00:00:31,958 --> 00:00:38,591
<i>One great Ninja was able to</i>
<i>imprison the monster,</i>

8
00:00:38,898 --> 00:00:40,923
<i>but died in the process.</i>

9
00:00:41,367 --> 00:00:47,203
<i>This Ninja was known as...</i>
<i>the Fourth Hokage.</i>

10
00:01:04,524 --> 00:01:05,548
Naruto!

11
00:01:05,758 --> 00:01:07,658
Why did you do such a thing?!

12
00:01:08,094 --> 00:01:10,085
You're really gonna get it this time!

13
00:01:15,768 --> 00:01:17,133
I don't care!

14
00:01:17,937 --> 00:01:19,461
You know your problem?

15
00:01:19,606 --> 00:01:21,836
You can't do the things I do!

16
00:01:22,142 --> 00:01:23,939
<i>Only I can do this!

17
00:01:24,144 --> 00:01:26,339
I'm better than all of you!